body: Another one from Ichihaya? Good stuff, good stuff. I can see how this will go already
Ichihaya is back! Now lets wait and see what he has for us this time !!

My guess is she's not really hypnotized at all; it's probably all an act. There's something making her yield her original stance that we'll see in another chapter down the line. That's the way these Ichihaya stories always tend to go anyway.
